value.value: アルカリフォスファターゼ血中濃度異常

アスパラギン酸アミノ基転移酵素の血中濃度異常

less than the average percentage of a volume of a blood sample occupied by red blood cells
赤血球の欠如

赤血球前駆細胞の欠如

白血球数の異常
any anomaly in the number of nucleated cells of the myeloid or lymphoid lineages, found in blood or other tissue
白血球数の増加
greater than normal number of nucleated cells of the myeloid or lymphoid lineages, found in blood or other tissue
好中球数の増加

greater than normal number of the immature or mature forms of a granular leukocyte that in its mature form has a nucleus with three to five lobes connected by slender threads of chromatin, and cytoplasm containing fine inconspicuous granules and stainable by neutral dyes
単球数の増加
greater count of the large, phagocytic mononuclear leukocytes produced in the vertebrate bone marrow and released into the blood

単球数の減少
reduced count of the large, phagocytic mononuclear leukocytes produced in the vertebrate bone marrow and released into the blood
平均赤血球容積の異常
deviation from normal for the average amount of space occupied by each red blood cell, calculated from the hematocrit and red cell count, in erythrocyte indices

definition.value: MCV is calculated by dividing the hematocrit by the total number of RBCs and multiplying this number by ten (10).

value.value: 血小板新生の異常
abnormal development of the non-nucleated cells of the blood (platelets, thrombocytes) involved in blood coagulation

原始心筒の形態異常

any anomaly in the characteristic surface outline or contour of the heart

心房中隔の形態異常
